</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="144" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,685,1756]" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1658,1684]" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Behounek, G. &amp; Ronkay, L. &amp; Ronkay, G." box="[322,579,1658,1684]" pageId="3" pageNumber="144" refId="ref1896" refString="Behounek, G., Ronkay, L. &amp; Ronkay, G. (2010) The Witt Catalogue. A taxonomic atlas of the Eurasian and North African Noctuoidea. Vol. 4. Plusiinae II. Heterocera Press, Budapest, 280 pp." type="book" year="2010">
Behounek 
<emphasis box="[442,498,1658,1684]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">et al.</emphasis>
(2010)
</bibRefCitation>
reported that 
<taxonomicName authority="Dufay, 1960" authorityName="Dufay" authorityYear="1960" box="[733,1084,1658,1684]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Abrostola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="144" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pacifica">
<emphasis box="[733,939,1658,1684]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">Abrostola pacifica</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Dufay, C." box="[946,1084,1658,1684]" pageId="3" pageNumber="144" pagination="303 - 313" refId="ref2107" refString="Dufay, C. (1960) Les espeses japoneses de genre Abrostola O. (Unca auct.) (Lepidoptera, Noctuidae, Plusiinae). Tinea, 5, 303 - 313." type="journal article" year="1960">Dufay, 1960</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is a new synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Dufay, 1958" authorityName="Dufay" authorityYear="1958" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Abrostola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="144" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="korbi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">Abrostola korbi</emphasis>
Dufay, 1958
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Kobayashi, H." box="[369,570,1694,1720]" pageId="3" pageNumber="144" pagination="274 - 277" refId="ref2143" refString="Kobayashi, H. (2009) Abrostola korbi Dufay was found from Primorye, Russia (Lepidoptera, Noctuidae, Plusiinae). Tinea, 20 (5), 274 - 277." type="journal article" year="2009">Kobayashi (2009)</bibRefCitation>
illustrated the male and female genitalia of these two studied species as valid species.
</paragraph>
